thread.title: Dennis

author: Dennis
title: Dennis
text: The people on the phone were very nice, very knowledgeable, and very helpfull. Was easy to place the order. Glass's arrived in a very timely matter. Prescription was correct. If there is one complaint is that they have so many frames to chose from and to find one that you like is hard. Need away to say put your picture then put frames on it to see what you look like. Will definitely order from Frame Direct again.
